snippet.title: Johnny Depp - Amber Heard Apology Video Goes Viral | Mango News
snippet.description:
Exclusive visuals of Johnny Depp and wife Amber Heard apologizing for robbed their pet dog inside Australia is going viral across the globe. However, the apology has attracted more criticism than appreciation with Johnny Depp not uttering the word sorry instead his wife Amber Heard is saying 'I'm truly sorry'.
